726731f-b.text:
Fresh Pond Road, east side, north of Sixtieth Ave., to 59th Drive,
showing in center of view, from left to right on the north side of 59th
Drive between Fresh Pond Road (new) and Fresh Pond Road (old), the Ankerbauer,alias Angelbach house and the T. Hallett house of 1852, subsequently
owned bv A. Sampson and Sons in 1891. View No. 2 shows Old Fresh Pond Road  at the right foreground.
July 1923.
View 2: January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
726731f-b.folder: Fresh Pond Road & 60th Avenue, Queens, NY
